  <brief_title>TLC D-99 and Ifosfamide in Metastatic Soft Tissue Sarcoma Patients</brief_title>
  <official_title>A Perspective Phase I and II Trial of Liposome-encapsulated Doxorubicin (TLC D-99) in Combination With Ifosfamide in Patients With Metastatic Soft Tissue Sarcoma</official_title>
  <sponsors>
    <lead_sponsor>
