  </oversight_info>
  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study is to determine the maximum tolerated dose of the TLC D-99 combined
      with ifosfamide and then the efficacy of this combination in terms of overall response rate,
      time to progression and time of response
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      The Maximum Tolerated Dose of the combination was determined and the Phase I terminated.

      Then, Phase II study started.
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
